<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1901-08-05T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1901-08-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="522" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d522">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Russell</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-08-05"><hi rend="italic">August 5,
                                1901</hi>.</date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>(Mr. Adee authorizes Mr. Russell to take charge of Colombian interests by
                            way of good offices, without assuming any representative character, if
                            he is requested by the Colombian minister to do so and the Government of
                            Venezuela acquiesces.)</p>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>